# PONG

This is a very BASIC Phyton 3 version of the classic game Pong. 

## How to play

Run pong.py
### Paddle Controls
| Paddle         | Up           | Down           |
|----------------|--------------|----------------|
| A (left-side)  | w            | s              |
| B (right-side) | up arrow key | down arrow key |

### Win Conditions
First player to 7 wins.